She looked around the room and saw a bed that looked nice and comfy.  
She walked over and curled up on top of the bed.  She thought a 
moment, had Rex changed his mind about Preds? would he be willing to 
accept peace?  she hoped so.  She would need a friend and an allie in 
this place.  She thought about CyberShark and prayed to the Matix 
that he was alright.  She fell asleep.
